#: ../../advanced/components/index.rst:153 d4df4e01ceb04d38a4ca6b794c9ada1f
msgid ""
"The GeoServer instance used by GeoNode, has a particular setup that allows "
"the two frameworks to correctly interact and exchange informations on users "
